## Development Status :open_book:

We have started the initial design phase and have a proof-of-concept for the core gameplay mechanics. Documentation and preliminary research have been conducted and can be provided upon request.

## Development Roadmap :nut_and_bolt:

### Overview

- **Total Estimated Duration:** 12 months
- **Full-Time Equivalent (FTE):** 4 FTE
- **Total Costs:** $100,000

### Milestone 1 — Game Design Document and Initial Prototype

- **Estimated duration:** 3 months
- **FTE:** 2
- **Costs:** $25,000

| Number | Deliverable | Specification |
| -----: | ----------- | ------------- |
| **0a.** | Documentation | Inline code documentation and a basic tutorial on setting up the game environment. |
| **0b.** | Testing and Testing Guide | Comprehensive unit tests for core functions, with a guide on running these tests. |
| **0c.** | Docker | Dockerfile for testing all functionality delivered with this milestone. |
| 1. | Game Design Document | Detailed GDD including gameplay mechanics, champion abilities, quest systems, and item specifications. |
| 2. | Basic Prototype | A basic prototype with limited gameplay mechanics and placeholder assets. Initial integration with blockchain for NFT item ownership. |

### Milestone 2 — Advanced Prototype and Smart Contracts

- **Estimated duration:** 3 months
- **FTE:** 2
- **Costs:** $25,000

| Number | Deliverable | Specification |
| -----: | ----------- | ------------- |
| **0a.** | Documentation | Updated documentation including new features and smart contract integration. |
| **0b.** | Testing and Testing Guide | Expanded unit tests covering new functionalities. |
| **0c.** | Docker | Updated Dockerfile for new functionalities. |
| 1. | Advanced Prototype | Expanded prototype with additional champions, enhanced quest system, and improved UI/UX. |
| 2. | Smart Contracts | Development and deployment of smart contracts for item ownership and marketplace functionalities. |

### Milestone 3 — Beta Launch

- **Estimated duration:** 3 months
- **FTE:** 2
- **Costs:** $25,000

| Number | Deliverable | Specification |
| -----: | ----------- | ------------- |
| **0a.** | Documentation | Comprehensive documentation for beta testers and developers. |
| **0b.** | Testing and Testing Guide | Full coverage of unit tests and integration tests. |
| **0c.** | Docker | Dockerfile for beta testing environment. |
| 1. | Beta Version | A fully functional beta version with a complete set of champions, items, quests, and marketplace. |
| 2. | User Feedback Integration | Collect and integrate feedback from beta testers to improve the game. |

### Milestone 4 — Full Launch

- **Estimated duration:** 3 months
- **FTE:** 2
- **Costs:** $25,000

| Number | Deliverable | Specification |
| -----: | ----------- | ------------- |
| **0a.** | Documentation | Final documentation including a comprehensive user guide and developer API documentation. |
| **0b.** | Testing and Testing Guide | Finalized testing guide with full test coverage. |
| **0c.** | Docker | Dockerfile for full production environment. |
| 1. | Full Game Launch | Complete version of the game with all features fully implemented, including additional champions, items, quests, and a polished user interface. |
| 2. | Community Building | Implement community engagement tools and events to build and support the player community. |
| 3. | Marketing and Outreach | Execute a marketing plan to attract a broader audience and ensure successful launch. |

## Future Plans

- **Long-term Maintenance and Development:**
  - We plan to finance the project’s long-term maintenance and development through in-game purchases, NFT sales, and potential partnerships with other blockchain projects.
  - Regular updates will be provided to introduce new content, balance gameplay, and fix any bugs.

- **Short-term Enhancements and Promotion:**
  - In the short term, we intend to enhance the game by adding more champions, quests, and items. We will also work on refining the user experience and integrating feedback from the community.
  - We will promote "Echoes of Eternity" through social media campaigns, collaborations with influencers, and by participating in gaming and blockchain events.

- **Long-term Plans and Intentions:**
  - Our long-term vision for "Echoes of Eternity" is to establish it as a leading game in the blockchain gaming space. We aim to create a vibrant community of players and continuously expand the game’s universe with new features and content.
  - We also plan to explore the possibilities of decentralized governance, allowing the community to have a say in the game’s future development.
